title: [Boreas Hills, Etesian Terrace]
description: The hill rises up high enough here to provide an unobstructed view of the meadow below.  Several tall mahogany trees dot the landscape as the hills continue to grow into the mountain.

The hill rises up high enough here to provide an unobstructed view of the meadow below bathed in moonlight.  Several tall mahogany trees dot the landscape as the hills continue to grow into the mountain.
